com.strategyobject.substrateclient.pallet.storage

Interface StorageNMap<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the value.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StorageNMapImpl

    public interface StorageNMap<V>
    Represents a storage of data in blockchain that persists between the blocks.

      • keysPaged

        PagedKeyIterator<V> keysPaged(int pageSize,
                              @NonNull
                              Object... keys)
        Returns an iterator of a key collection, each item of which contains the remaining keys of the entry. Each item of the iterator contains a key collection with size equal to the page's size or smaller in case of the last page and the total number isn't multiple of the page's size.
        Parameters:
        pageSize - number of items in collection per page.
        keys - some keys of the storage's entry. Note: all the keys must follow the same strict order as their sequence in the storage.
        Returns:
        iterator of key collections.
